:: overlay widgets [widget nobr]
/* adds an overlay to the following "continue button".

<<overlay "int">>

_args[0] = the color of overlay you want
*/
<<widget "overlay">>
    <<set $overlays.push(_args[0])>>
<</widget>>

/* for when there's no overlay, just call this as an empty function. add this as a buffer when the overlays get wonky

<<nooverlay>>
*/
<<widget "nooverlay">>
    <<set $overlays.push(false)>>
<</widget>>